headline: Honeywell rises as BofA upgrades stock to Buy on a return to positive revisions
summary: Investing.com -- Bank of America (BofA) has upgraded Honeywell (NASDAQ:HON) to Buy from Neutral and raised its price objective on the stock to $250 from $210, citing a return to stable or positive earnings revisions following a solid first-quarter beat.
